commit.message: Adds ability to specify absolute import only to pockets.inspect.resolve()
Changes mappify() to return an empty dict if passed None
Adds string.splitify() and collections.is_mappy(). Drops support for 2.6 and 3.3
Updates pockets.inspect.import_star() so that it returns a map of attrs instead of setting them on the module
Uses actual module to hoist, instead of module name
Better exception reporting in pockets.inspect.resolve(), pockets.inspect.hoist_submodules() now updates __all__ by default
More restrictive error handling in pockets.inspect.resolve()
Makes inspect.resolve() more robust, adds hoist_submodules and import_submodules
Attempts to fix travis, since tox dropped 3.3 support
Fixes bug in inspect.resolve() where deeply nested modules would not resolve
